name: Firm Capital Property Trust
longDescription: Firm Capital Property Trust is a Canada-based open-ended real estate investment trust. The company operates in five reportable segments: Grocery Anchored Retail, Non-Grocery Anchored Retail, Industrial, Multi-Residential, and Core Service Office Provider. A vast majority of its revenues are derived from the Grocery anchored retail segment.
